@startuml
' Developer-journey activity swim lane. Lane declared before start; nodes use the
' label-only link form (see schema.md). Render: skills/gcodetour-author/scripts/render-diagrams.sh
!theme bluegray
' Opaque background so the diagram reads on any VS Code editor theme (the panel
' background follows the reader's theme; C4 diagrams bake this automatically).
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
' Roboto is installed into the renderer image and embedded into the SVG.
skinparam defaultFontName Roboto

title gCodeTour — developer journey

|Developer|
start
:[[ct://el/open Open a workspace with tours]];
:[[ct://el/start Start a tour]];
|Extension|
:[[ct://el/discover Discover .tour files]];
:[[ct://el/render Render step in a comment thread]];
:[[ct://el/diagramstep Show synchronized diagram]];
|Developer|
:[[ct://el/navigate Navigate next / previous]];
stop

@enduml
